om/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6229833c-4cf2-4d79-b4d0-ced5f5ebb24d.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0272","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0126","title":"SGI IRIX xterm 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 及 Solaris 5.5.1 X11R6.3 系统中 xterm 终端模拟器与 Xaw 部件库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xterm 的 `-xrm` 参数传递超长资源字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有本地账号，攻击复杂度较低，影响 SGI IRIX 和 Solaris 等 UNIX 系统的 X11R6.3 环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0126"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.733","remediation":"移除 xterm 的 SUID 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xterm`，防止本地用户通过 `-xrm` 参数以 root 权限执行任意代码。同时升级 Solaris 至 5.5.1 以上补丁版本，或从 IRIX 厂商处获取 xterm 安全修补程序。如不使用 Xaw 库程序，建议将其一并移除或降权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-010.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/338","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83078/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--160f8a79-d4d5-4c33-8fab-f1a31520e3d2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0271","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0125","title":"SGI IRIX mailx 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 mailx 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序对用户输入的数据长度缺乏充分校验，当攻击者向 mailx 程序传入特制的超长参数时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致程序异常崩溃。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞实现权限提升，获取 root 权限。该漏洞同样影响 RedHat Linux 4.2 和 Solaris 2.6 系统。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0125"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.563","remediation":"SGI IRIX 用户请安装 SGI 安全公告 19980605-01-PX 提供的 mailx 补丁；RedHat Linux 4.2 用户升级 mailx 到已修复版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装 Sun 官方 mailx 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 mailx 的 setuid 位：chmod u-s /bin/mailx。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19312","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0125","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0125.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0270","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0124","title":"UMN Gopher 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"UMN Gopher 及 Gopher+ 服务程序（1.12 和 2.0x 版本）存在未授权任意文件读取漏洞。由于 gopherd 守护进程未能对文件访问请求进行充分的权限校验，攻击者可以利用该缺陷绕过访问限制，读取 gopher 守护进程可访问范围内的任意系统文件，包括敏感配置信息。此漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，攻击难度低，对系统机密性构成严重威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0124"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.420","remediation":"升级 UMN gopher 至 2.0.18 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。同时修改 gopherd 配置文件，设置根目录为仅含公开内容的隔离路径（如 /var/gopher），并使用 chroot 机制限制守护进程访问范围。通过文件系统权限确保 gopher 运行用户（如 nobody）对 /etc/passwd 等敏感文件无读取权限。如无需对外提供 Gopher 服务，建议直接停止并卸载 gopherd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0124"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0269","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0269.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0123","title":"Linux mailx 条件竞争漏洞","description":"Linux mailx 命令存在竞态条件漏洞，本地用户通过利用邮件处理过程中临时文件的竞争条件，可读取其他用户的文件内容。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 发行版（如 Slackware Linux），攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较高。CVSS 评分 3.7，危害等级低。建议升级软件版本或限制本地用户访问权限以缓解风险。","severity":"LOW","score":3.7,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0123"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1995-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.280","remediation":"升级 mailx 到 8.1.2 及以上版本，或替换为 mutt/Heirloom mailx 等不受影响的邮件客户端。临时缓解措施包括移除 mailx 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /bin/mail）并通过 PAM 或 sudo 限制 mailx 执行权限，但会影响正常邮件读取功能，建议尽快完成版本升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0123"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0269.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0268","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0268.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0122","title":"IBM AIX lchangelv 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2 系统中的 /usr/sbin/lchangelv 工具存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码。攻击者需要通过本地账户登录系统，向 lchangelv 程序提交特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖返回地址或函数指针劫持进程控制流。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击前提是拥有本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0122"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.147","remediation":"IBM AIX 4.2 用户应立即升级至 AIX 4.3.3 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复；或安装对应 APAR 补丁包。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 500 /usr/sbin/lchangelv` 移除 setuid 位，限制普通用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0122","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0122.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ccc7-4g5p-rggh/GHSA-ccc7-4g5p-rggh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0122.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--772eac60-d912-4492-9f00-76b00cf63353.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0268.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0267","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0121","title":"CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"dtaction 是 CDE（通用桌面环境）工具集中的命令执行组件，其存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 dtaction 提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 CDE 的多款 Unix 系统（包括 Solaris、HP-UX、AIX 等），CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0121"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.013","remediation":"立即移除 dtaction 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`，阻断本地普通用户以 root 权限执行。若业务允许，建议禁用 CDE 桌面环境（`/etc/init.d/dtlogin stop && chkconfig dtlogin off` 或相应平台等价操作）。各 Unix 厂商补丁：Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00192 对应补丁 (patch ID 107021-01+)；HP-UX 安装 HPSBUX9909-103 对应补丁；AIX 安装 APAR IY08886 补丁；IRIX 升级至 6.5.15 或更高版本。同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，防止非受信用户获得交互式 shell 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0266","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0120","title":"Sun Solaris utmp 文件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 utmp 文件存在权限配置不当漏洞。当该文件被设置为非 root 用户可写时，本地攻击者可修改 utmp 文件内容，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris 系统，需要攻击者拥有本地账户权限，攻击者可通过构造特制的 utmp 记录实现权限提升，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0120"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.890","remediation":"确保 utmp 文件仅 root 可写：执行 `chmod 644 /var/adm/utmp` 或 `chmod 644 /etc/utmp` 移除其他用户的写权限，同时 `chown root:root /var/adm/utmp` 确保文件属主为 root。升级到已修复此问题的 SunOS/Solaris 安全补丁版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/126"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0265","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0119","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 共享资源未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 beta 版本存在权限验证缺陷，由于系统对共享资源的访问控制机制不完善，任意用户无需身份认证即可读取或删除网络共享目录中的文件。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 beta 测试版系统，攻击者可通过 SMB 协议远程访问目标主机上的共享资源，导致敏感信息泄露或数据丢失，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0119"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.760","remediation":"立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 beta 至 Windows NT 4.0 RTM 正式版，并安装最新 Service Pack 6a。为所有共享目录设置明确的 ACL 权限，禁止 Everyone 组具有读写权限，将共享目录所在分区转换为 NTFS 文件系统以启用更细粒度的访问控制，同时在注册表中将 RestrictAnonymous 键值设置为 1 以限制匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/11"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0263","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0263.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0694","title":"IBM AIX ptrace 系统调用本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统中的 ptrace 系统调用存在缺陷，本地攻击者可通过向目标系统发起特制的 ptrace 调用来触发该漏洞，导致系统内核崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AIX 多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地用户权限方可利用，无法远程触发，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0694"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.820","remediation":"安装 IBM AIX APAR IX68314 补丁，或将 AIX 升级至 4.3.3 Maintenance Level 9 及以上版本。如无法立即打补丁，可通过限制非授权用户本地登录、使用 chdev 禁用不必要的调试接口等措施降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-055.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0694","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0694.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vg2c-63m3-5wwm/GHSA-vg2c-63m3-5wwm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84474/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--06fdb7a2-f512-4bc3-ba75-667344476ce2.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0263.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0693","title":"多厂商 CDE ToolTalk 共享库 TT_SESSION 环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 共享库处理 TT_SESSION 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Digital UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地账号方可利用，无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0693"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.690","remediation":"建议安装各厂商当年发布的安全补丁：Sun Solaris 用户安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 对应补丁(如 107256-xx)；IBM AIX 4.3.2 用户安装 APAR IY07617；HP-UX 用户应用 HPSBUX9909-103 补丁；SGI IRIX 6.5.14 用户安装 SGI 安全补丁；Compaq DIGITAL UNIX 4.0 用户安装对应安全修补包。如无法立即打补丁，可将 ToolTalk 相关二进制文件移除 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施，或禁用 CDE 环境中的 ToolTalk 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/641","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A4374","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19501","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0693","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0693.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0118","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 infod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 系统的 infod 组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 X display 机制向 infod 服务发送特制请求，利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.630","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM AIX 4.3.3 及以上受支持版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 IX72357。如无需 infod 服务，可执行 `stopsrc -t infod` 停止该服务并通过注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中相关行禁用，以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91158980826979&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19287","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0118","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6c29fe92-c11f-40b7-bc14-92d730f9e4fc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0260","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0260.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0117","title":"IBM AIX passwd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 passwd 命令存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于 passwd 程序在处理用户密码更改操作时未充分检查权限，本地普通用户可通过执行特制的 passwd 命令利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需身份认证即可提权至 root，从而完全控制系统。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0117"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-03-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.490","remediation":"立即安装 IBM AIX 对应版本的 APAR 安全补丁（如 APAR IX47474 或更新版本），或升级至 AIX 4.1 及以上已修复版本。临时缓解措施可移除 passwd 命令的 SUID 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/passwd），但可能导致普通用户无法自行修改密码，需通过 root 管理员代为操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0117"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0260.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0259","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0259.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0116","title":"多种厂商 TCP/IP SYN Flood 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"TCP SYN Flood 是一种经典的拒绝服务攻击方式，攻击者利用 TCP 三次握手机制，向目标服务器发送大量伪造源地址的 SYN 请求包，服务器为每个请求分配资源并返回 SYN+ACK 包，但因无法收到最终的 ACK 确认包而导致连接半开状态持续占用系统资源，最终耗尽服务器连接队列，导致正常用户无法访问服务。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2.5/4.1/4.2 等早期操作系统版本，攻击者无需认证即可发起攻击，是网络层拒绝服务攻击的典型代表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0116"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.367","remediation":"启用 TCP SYN Cookies（如 Linux 设置 net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）；缩短 SYN 超时时间（如设置 net.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries=1）；增大半连接队列（如设置 net.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog=1024）。AIX 系统应安装对应补丁程序 APAR IX73380，并在边界防火墙上限制单位时间内新连接速率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/136","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0116","https://github.com/nbrito/research/blob/f070ce78f917d962de8df74cc7a841f1cbbcfa00/ddos/1996/CVE-1999-0116/README.md","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0116.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-qfp8-p689-pjw7/GHSA-qfp8-p689-pjw7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2009/CVE-2009-2318.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-2007-6040.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0259.toml"}]